{"tid":50514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宜家地櫃壓死美國3小童　賠近4億港元和解","createTime":"2016-12-22T12:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T06:25:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"328c927ca0bf4a5f7cb20479f67f9e1dc2ab9d56","tid":50514,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/photo/bknint-20161222151223301-1222_17011_001_01p.jpg?20161222171753\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161222%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161222151223301-1222_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20161222171753&h=43edfff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/photo/bknint-20161222151223301-1222_17011_001_02p.jpg?20161222171753\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161222%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161222151223301-1222_17011_001_02p.jpg%3F20161222171753&h=1bf356df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宜家家居答允就3名受害小童作出賠償，包括泰特（右）。（資料圖片）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=jR0cHZac4yDs2OhOEsM1kgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=ad3e500e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 全球最大傢俬零售商、瑞典宜家家居（IKEA）生產的Malm系列坐地抽屜櫃，在美國已導致多宗倒下壓死小童意外。該公司日前與其中3名受害小童的家屬達成和解，向他們賠償合共5000萬美元（約3.9億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n3名受害小童年齡介乎22個月大至2歲，分別於前年2月、6月，以及今年2月不幸遭Malm系列坐地櫃壓死。他們的家人早前入稟向宜家家居索償，至近日後者終願意賠償，3名受害小童家人將平分該筆賠償。宜家同時會以3名小童名義，捐出15萬美元給兒童醫院及非牟利組織。家屬均稱，賠償金無法挽回已逝孩子的性命，但希望廠家和其他家長引以為鑑。<br />\n<br />\n自1989年以來，各地共發生14宗兒童遭Malm系列抽屜櫃壓死或壓傷的意外。今年2月，美國明尼蘇達州22個月大男童泰特，被該款地櫃壓着良久才被發現，返魂乏術。宜家家居其後於6月宣布全球回收至少2900萬個有潛在危險的坐地櫃，並宣布將Malm系列下架。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/bknint-20161222151223301-1222_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161222%2Fbknint-20161222151223301-1222_17011_001.html&d=jR0cHZac4yDs2OhOEsM1kgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=79cc5570\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/bknint-20161222151223301-1222_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1a2f25318e98dc7520d38eeb02c3f6f44c6b06af","tid":50514,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:54:12.000Z","msg":"回收唔包香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9c9afb66fef5351bca5cb82610d0a0fd16ac6d","tid":50514,"uid":49015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回收唔包香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜有回收包香港？"},{"pid":"2b685e3af83eec535dd1bc2ee9741ad6d24e87ef","tid":50514,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回收唔包香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人？咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c69fa80d8779fc88c2d44fd57059c499a18ef2","tid":50514,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回收唔包香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n包支那的話，應該突然死成百萬人，連老人家都壓死。"},{"pid":"14aec6bd26e5e2bc913d138dff12a6f58e2d72cf","tid":50514,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>回收唔包香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人？咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正名為港豬"},{"pid":"61a61ca0f1660dccf21e105f3e52d452b8825df3","tid":50514,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:59:38.000Z","msg":"遲下個槌仔揼到自己又可以索償"},{"pid":"2b8ccc7a6936bf4fd75f710216d12761f65eedda","tid":50514,"uid":1672,"like":0,